g.text: Open Window to Enter:
URLs to Agent files and Config file
Dynamic List for Device Specific Credentials with option to use the same credentials for all selected devices
Offer option: Onload with historical Data from Data Mailbox if available
Trigger Download of Agent Files
Loop over all selected devices: Get call to Talk2M with individual device credentials to trigger the download of the files
Check if the files are present and if A dummy device exists for the data Mailbox sync functionality
Loop over all selected devices ( until all devices downloaded the files or timeout is reached):
If the files are present and no dummy device is present for the Datamailbox Sync:
restart the device, approve registration for "HMS-Flexy-{SERIAL}", flag as registered; Add ExternalID "HMS-Talk2M-{SERIAL}" to the device
If the files are present and a dummy device is already present for the Datamailbox Sync:
restart the device, approve registration for "HMS-Flexy-{SERIAL}", add "HMS-Flexy-{SERIAL}" as external ID to the dummy device
Provide Result List per device:
Successful
Successful and merged with exising dummy device;
Time Out: files were not successfully downloaded

g.text: Check if a device already exists
Loop over devices to see if there is already a device with the externalId "HMS-Flexy-{SERIAL}" or "HMS-Talk2M-{SERIAL}"
create new or combine devices
If there is a device with the repective external ID "HMS-Flexy-{SERIAL}" also add the "HMS-Talk2M-{SERIAL} to it
If there is a device with the repective external ID "HMS-Talk2M-{SERIAL}" nothing needs to be done
If there is not related device, create new dummy device includiing regisration approval
Create Job for devices
Create the sync job for the list of devices with the respective "HMS-Talk2M-{SERIAL}
